  "title": "Client Advisor | Farming Nursery / Plantation / Landscape Design",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Junior / Senior Sales Executive [ Plantation | Landscaping ]</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>5 Days, 8.30am-5.30pm</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic Salary: $2,400 - $3,800 + 14 Days AL</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>After Probation Will Entitled to Group Sales Incentive [ $600-$2,000 Per Month ]</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Office is at Bedok, Singapore [ East ]</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Company Background:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Landscaping solutions for businesses and industry in financial, healthcare, commercial property, residential property, retail and education.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Summary:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Seeking a Sales Executive </strong>who can combine plant knowledge with sales acumen to deliver <strong>tailored indoor plant and landscaping solutions.</strong></li>\n  <li>You’ll play a key role in helping businesses and homeowners create environments that are healthier, greener, and more inspiring.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><strong>Requirements:</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Option 1: Entry level but with at least diploma in <strong>Landscape Architecture, Horticulture, Agriculture or related fields</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Option 2: Those with <strong>2 years of industry experience</strong> ( plants, landscape design, horticulture, or related sales) but willing switch to sales or service advisor role.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><strong>Job Scopes</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Leverage your <strong>horticulture / landscape expertise</strong> to understand client needs and recommend suitable plant solutions.</li>\n  <li>Grow our client base by identifying and securing new business opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Provide professional consultation, proposals, and creative plant concepts to clients.</li>\n  <li>Manage and deepen client relationships to ensure long-term satisfaction.</li>\n  <li>Negotiate and close deals to achieve sales targets and revenue growth.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with our operations and design teams to deliver seamless solutions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>#SCR-carson-cheong</p>\n<p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p>\n<p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p>",
